{"tid":794460,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"你地敢唔敢同親戚講自己讀緊咩學校？","createTime":"2018-08-26T09:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T10:13:12.000Z","uid":112551,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"596552637741dd16bfb7c49a994312af73258637","tid":794460,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:10:44.000Z","msg":"每次親戚聚會都被人問自己讀緊咩學校，我都只好細細聲講，因為以前中學個校名真係好柒又普通唔出名，講出來會被人起底再笑。<br />\n<br />\n近派有個親戚個女讀VTC，我見佢都唔想透露咁多，我都唔想追問。<br />\n<br />\n不過有一次約另一親戚個仔，佢個仔每次約我地去酒樓食野都遲到，之後話「唔好意思呀，我岩岩大學放學，塔地鐵遲咗啲。」好似喺到show off自己讀緊大學。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要著住大學Tee，邊間大學我諗大家都估到啦。<br />\n<br />\n你地敢唔敢同親戚講自己讀緊咩學校？被人問到點答？"},{"pid":"b82e9c11917fd710b48f7793a57ac58aee377017","tid":794460,"uid":157980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:15:25.000Z","msg":"proud of my school?"},{"pid":"548dbfdecf36508156e393ff75aef2b8074b957d","tid":794460,"uid":79931,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:16:18.000Z","msg":"點解要介意<br />\nVTC同Kong U grad的人工都是差唔多<br />\n（醫科除外）"},{"pid":"12187c64ad181418daf01766989e39e399a74bc9","tid":794460,"uid":77643,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:18:01.000Z","msg":"shitty<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091a7a0392e1c24e5f8ff33f5fbfd8c789c3d486","tid":794460,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:18:22.000Z","msg":"讀咩科先？乞食科就收皮啦 有乜咁巴閉"},{"pid":"abfc59dc0fd70b07229699eb0dccdb7d7fdc7781","tid":794460,"uid":46494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"敢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c26902f1761794a4fe1c7425a2b423e9e3aacd9","tid":794460,"uid":3688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c